desc: High quality Fender Rhodes, Wurlitzer and Hohner electric piano parts for owners & restorers across the UK & Europe. No other pianos in the world can recreate the unique blend of tone and harmonics that these pianos produce, and it’s a passion for these distinctive sounds that compelled us to build a business.
